name: Immaculate Conception
description: Took and edited this photo almost 9 years ago exactly. Giving this piece to every collector of my work for Christmas.  In July of 1929 the Shrine of Our Lady of Lourdes was dedicated in New Lebanon with better then 9,000 people in attendance. The Shrine is kept up by people who volunteer from the parish, using donations from those who appreciate this lovely devotional place. 2021
